{
  "stem": "23155.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "For instance, bread was delivered on a hearse, the old fashioned hearse, like used to be in Europe.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "They were drawn by horses, of course.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "So instead of the horses, there were two men.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "And the bread was stacked up in the hearse.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "So you saw that on the, on the street.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "You saw girls going to work in the gardens.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "You saw people cleaning the street.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "Everybody did something.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "We all worked, no matter what.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "But everybody was very busy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "They had two homes for young boys.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "And they had, they had homes for sick people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "We had mentally ill.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "We had scarlet fever, typhoid, and-- well, I don't know you say that in English-- encephalitis.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "That's a brain-- I think the cover of the brain is an infection there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "And, and then we had police, Jewish police.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "And they took young, handsome men.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "And they dressed them up in a uniform.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "It was like in an operetta-- you know, the high hats with epaulettes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "And they didn't have much of a power, but they would be there when we would line up for our food.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "So people would be, you know, in line, or that if somebody started-- maybe if they have a little fight or something.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "So they were there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 81,
      "text": "We did also have gendarmes, Czech police.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 82,
      "text": "And then we had the SS who really weren't-- it only-- they only were in, at headquarters.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 83,
      "text": "We had a government.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 84,
      "text": "There was the elder of the Jews.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 85,
      "text": "And then you had the finance department, and the agriculture department, and the school department.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 86,
      "text": "I mean, it really was like a city or a state on itself.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At that time, his name was Edelstein-- Jacob Edelstein.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
